{"ts": "2026-06-08T03:57:34.955130+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 4c386b25d56ec24baa2939d718ff0c3708c8627b)", "id": "lc_b10a650d-ef3c-4bef-8836-bb20ec291eb1"}, {"type": "text", "text": "name: release-main\n\non:\n  push:\n    branches: [main]\n\njobs:\n  ci:\n    runs-on: ${{ matrix.os }}\n\n    strategy:\n      matrix:\n        os: [ubuntu-latest]\n\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout 🛎\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0\n\n      - name: Setup node env 🏗\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version-file: '.nvmrc'\n          check-latest: true\n\n      - name: Setup pnpm 📦\n        uses: pnpm/action-setup@v4\n        with:\n          package_json_file: package.json\n\n      - name: Install dependencies 📦\n        run: pnpm install\n\n      - name: Run linter 👀\n        run: pnpm run lint-fix\n\n      - name: Run tests 🧪\n        run: pnpm run test:unit\n\n      - name: Build\n        run: pnpm run build\n  release:\n    runs-on: ${{ matrix.os }}\n    needs: ci\n\n    permissions:\n      id-token: write\n      contents: write    \n\n    strategy:\n      matrix:\n        os: [ubuntu-latest]\n\n    steps:\n      - name: Checkout 🛎\n        uses: actions/checkout@v4\n        with:\n          fetch-depth: 0\n\n      - name: Setup node env 🏗\n        uses: actions/setup-node@v4\n        with:\n          node-version-file: '.nvmrc'\n          check-latest: true\n\n      - name: Setup pnpm 📦\n        uses: pnpm/action-setup@v4\n        with:\n          package_json_file: package.json\n\n      - name: Install dependencies 📦\n        run: pnpm install\n\n      - name: Install semantic-release extra plugins 📦\n        run: pnpm install --save-dev semantic-release @semantic-release/changelog @semantic-release/git\n\n      - name: Release\n        env:\n          GITHUB_TOKEN: ${{ secrets.GITHUB_TOKEN }}\n        run: npx semantic-release\n", "id": "lc_0263a0d8-ac10-4e28-a87e-28b98c1a1f25"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "7733d196-6b61-4f74-8273-d92d79a6b917", "tool_call_id": "call_00_Gsb5vJEMgcpIerA9UDOF2404", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-08T03:57:48.867078+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Answer: Contributors **must use pnpm**; npm is **not** acceptable.\n\n### Evidence from the repository\n\n1. **`package.json` – hard enforcement via `only-allow`**  \n   The `preinstall` script runs `npx only-allow pnpm`. This package blocks any install attempt with a package manager other than pnpm. If a contributor runs `npm install`, it will fail with an error instructing them to use pnpm.\n\n2. **`package.json` – declared package manager**  \n   The file includes `\"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\"`. This field tells Corepack (and other tooling) that pnpm is the expected package manager and which version to use.\n\n3. **Lockfile**  \n   The repository contains a `pnpm-lock.yaml` (207 KB) and has **no** `package-lock.json` or `yarn.lock`. This is the canonical lockfile for pnpm and signals that dependencies are managed exclusively with pnpm.\n\n4. **README instructions**  \n   All project-setup and script commands are shown with `pnpm` (e.g., `pnpm install`, `pnpm run dev`, `pnpm run build`). No npm equivalents are given.\n\n5. **CI/CD workflow (`.github/workflows/release.yml`)**  \n   The release pipeline uses `pnpm/action-setup@v4` and runs every task through pnpm (`pnpm install`, `pnpm run lint-fix`, `pnpm run test:unit`, `pnpm run build`). npm is never called.\n\n### Bottom line\nThe repository is locked to pnpm through multiple deliberate mechanisms—the `only-allow` preinstall guard, the `packageManager` field, the pnpm-only lockfile, documentation, and CI. There is no provision for using npm.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 818, "prompt_tokens": 9082, "total_tokens": 9900, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 424, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 8448}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 8448, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 634}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "c9b60293-dbb4-4ecc-8381-a7ee00aa0b53", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea560-f36c-7a13-8d10-08ddf36a84bf-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 9082, "output_tokens": 818, "total_tokens": 9900, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 8448}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 424}}}}]}}}
